{"word":"H309 - אָחַר - ʼâchar - aw-khar' - Continue","slug":"H309","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָחַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼâchar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-khar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Continue"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05D7;&#x05E8; - 'a&#x0302;char</b> - <i>aw-khar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>loiter</i> (that is, <i>be behind</i>); by implication to <i>procrastinate: - </i>continue, defer, delay, hinder, be late (slack), stay (there), tarry (longer)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H268\">H268</a>, <a href=\"#/H310\">H310</a>, <a href=\"#/H312\">H312</a>, <a href=\"#/H313\">H313</a>, <a href=\"#/H314\">H314</a>, <a href=\"#/H315\">H315</a>, <a href=\"#/H316\">H316</a>, <a href=\"#/H3186\">H3186</a>, <a href=\"#/H319\">H319</a>, <a href=\"#/H322\">H322</a>, <a href=\"#/H323\">H323</a>, <a href=\"#/H325\">H325</a>, <a href=\"#/H326\">H326</a>, <a href=\"#/H327\">H327</a>"}]}